Job description 1:

- Customer requirement analysis as it pertains to automotive cybersecurity
Create/Maintain Threat and Risk Assessment (TARA) of automotive systems
Define cybersecurity requirements for projects
Specification, design, and review of the security architecture with the system/software team
Create/Maintain DIA (Development Interface Agreement)
Conduct security feasibility and risk analysis for security architecture
Support the test strategy definition to exercise the security system
Plan, design, and execute fuzz and penetration testing
Train and coach of junior engineers
Aid in creation/maintenance of cybersecurity process in the organization
Support cybersecurity incident detection and investigation

